Q-history with date and time?

A-HISTTIMEFORMAT="%d/%m/%y %T ".

Q-how to update history if entered manually in /home/adhoc/.bash_history(without reboot and logout)?

A-open the file .bash_history through gedit
and update it manually.

Q-How create multiple files and folder at once in windows? 

A-type in command line>

                                                     for /L %i in (1,1,5) do (mkdir a%i)
